name: Kathy Thompson
text: My house burned and after a lengthy stay at a motel I finally got an apt but had nothing. They helped me with some food , and some linens and are trying to help me get a much needed bed and dresser. They are a small thrift shop but they have big hearts that will try to help as much as possible. I'm very grateful to them for what they have done to help me get settled into my apt.
